  "texts": [
    "The study uses Mälardalen University benchmarks [95] to validate the method, demonstrating improved WCET accuracy and tightness in 69% of benchmarks, with a safeness percentage over 60%.",
    "SVR is highlighted for its capability to predict complex variables.",
    "Unlike traditional methods, SVR maps sample space into a high-dimensional feature space using a kernel function.",
    "The Legendre orthogonal functions, known for their mathematical properties, are utilized as the SVR kernel to handle non-linear relationships effectively.Zhang et al. [96] explore dynamic cache locking and task scheduling in singlecore embedded systems.",
    "Cache locking is utilized to enhance the predictability of the WCET by locking critical contents in the cache, which cannot be evicted until unlocked."
